    <name>AndroidPdfViewer</name>
    <description>An Android PDF Library provides developers with the tools to display, manipulate,
        and create PDF files in Android applications. These libraries make it easier to handle PDFs
        in an efficient and user-friendly way without needing to develop complex PDF rendering from
        scratch. Android PDF libraries can handle a variety of tasks such as displaying PDF pages,
        zooming, annotating, and handling text selection.
    </description>

